@startuml cdc-and-event-flow
title AdScale — потоки данных: CDC, impression, recovery

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 14
skinparam BoxPadding 8

actor "Advertiser" as Adv
participant "Campaign\nService" as Camp
database "Campaign\nPostgreSQL" as CampDb
participant "Debezium\n(CDC)" as Deb
queue "Kafka" as K
database "Redis\nCluster" as Redis
participant "Bidding\nService" as Bid

== Сценарий 1. CDC — изменение кампании ==

Adv -> Camp: PUT /campaigns/123\n{ bid_ceiling_kop: ... }
activate Camp
Camp -> CampDb: UPDATE campaigns SET ... WHERE id=123
CampDb --> Camp: OK
Camp --> Adv: 200 OK
deactivate Camp

CampDb ->> Deb: WAL change (logical replication)
activate Deb
Deb ->> K: publish cdc.campaign.v1\n{ campaign_id: 123, before, after }
deactivate Deb

K -> Bid: consume cdc.campaign.v1
activate Bid
Bid -> Redis: DEL campaign:{123}
Redis --> Bid: OK
Bid -> K: commit offset
deactivate Bid

note right of Bid
  Следующий cache miss
  подтянет свежие данные read-through
  из read-replica Campaign PostgreSQL.
end note

== Сценарий 2. Impression — fan-out на трёх consumer'ов ==

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Delivery\nService" as Del
participant "Statistics\nService" as Stats
participant "Financial\nService" as Fin
database "ClickHouse" as CH
database "Finance\nPostgreSQL" as FinDb

User -> Del: HTTPS GET creative
activate Del
Del --> User: 200 OK + ad
Del -> Del: формирует event с event_id (UUID), trace_id
Del ->> K: publish delivery.impression.v1\n(key=campaign_id, acks=all)
deactivate Del

note right of K
  RF=3, min.insync.replicas=2,
  партиционирование по campaign_id.
  Три независимые consumer-группы
  читают одно событие.
end note

par Statistics Service
  K -> Stats: poll delivery.impression.v1
  activate Stats
  Stats -> Stats: dedup by event_id\n(Redis SET NX EX)
  Stats -> Stats: оконная агрегация (1m / 5m / 1h)
  Stats -> CH: INSERT aggregates
  Stats -> K: commit offset
  deactivate Stats
also Financial Service (биллинг)
  K -> Fin: poll delivery.impression.v1
  activate Fin
  Fin -> FinDb: BEGIN\n  INSERT billing_transactions (event_id, ...)\n  ON CONFLICT (event_id) DO NOTHING\n  UPDATE wallets SET balance_kop = balance_kop - amount_kop\nCOMMIT
  FinDb --> Fin: OK
  Fin ->> K: publish billing.transaction.v1 (audit)
  Fin -> K: commit offset
  deactivate Fin
also Bidding Service (обновление Redis-счётчиков)
  K -> Bid: poll delivery.impression.v1
  activate Bid
  Bid -> Bid: dedup by event_id
  Bid -> Redis: INCRBY budget:{campaign_id} -amount_kop
  Bid -> Redis: INCR freqcap:{user}:{campaign}
  Bid -> K: commit offset
  deactivate Bid
end

note left of K
  Replay: при сбое любого consumer
  можно перечитать события из retention окна.
  Idempotent Consumer защищает от двойной обработки.
end note

== Сценарий 3. Восстановление проекции из Kafka ==

participant "Financial Service\n(new pod)" as FinNew

note over FinNew, FinDb
  После сбоя Financial Service:
  под рестартует, читает с последнего
  закоммиченного offset'а.
end note

FinNew -> K: poll from last committed offset
K --> FinNew: события за окно lag
FinNew -> FinDb: idempotent INSERT'ы (ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING)
note right of FinNew
  Дубликаты, успевшие обработаться
  до сбоя, отклоняются по unique(event_id).
  Двойного списания не происходит.
end note

@enduml
